# GOBS Golf — Manual Test Tracker

*Living document for verifying ship deploys on the live app. Update statuses as features land.*

*Last updated: May 7, 2026*

---

## How to use this doc

- Tests run on the deployed app (gobs-golf.vercel.app) on a real phone after Vercel finishes deploying
- Mark each test:
  - **✅ Pass** with date
  - **❌ Fail** with date and short note (paste back to Claude for triage)
  - **⏳ Pending** if not yet run
- Sections are organized by phase and batch — append new sections at the bottom as work ships
- When a phase is fully verified, the section can collapse to a single "✅ Verified [date]" summary line if you want to keep this doc lean

